<html lang="en">
<head>
    {% include '../components/global_head.njk' %}
</head>
    <body>
        {% include '../components/nav.njk' %}
        <div id="wrap"> {# Content minimum height wrapper, place between nav and footer #}

        <div class='hero-with-cta splash-big' style='background-color: #0c152a'>
            {# Hero banner #}
            <div class='hero-cta'>
                {# Hero Call to Action #}
                <div  class='flex-columns center-content large-spacer mobile-spacer-small hero-margins'  >
                    <div class='campaign-major-message large-spacer mobile-spacer-small' >
                        <span>
                        {{splashTitle}}
                        <br> <h4 style='font-weight: 200'>{{marketTargetedTagline}}</h4>
                        </span> 
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        {% include '../components/cta/herocda.njk' %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class='campaign-pain skeleton block-full '>
            {# Speak to pain! header#}
            <div class='block-quote' style='padding-top:110px; padding-bottom:90px'>
                <span>{{majorArgument}}</span>
            </div>
            {#Three images and three ways we can help#}
            <div class='flex-columns' style='padding-left: 10%; padding-right:10%;'> 
                <div>
                        <div style="background-image: url({{imageOneOffer}}); background-size: cover; width:100%; aspect-ratio: 2.05"></div>
                    <div Style='text-align:center; padding-bottom:30px'>
                        {# Speak to pain text 1#}
                        <br>{{offerOne}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                        <div style="background-image: url({{imageTwoOffer}}); background-size: cover; width:100%; aspect-ratio: 2.05"></div>
                    <div Style='text-align:center; padding-bottom:30px'>
                            {# Speak to pain text 1#}
                            <br>{{offerTwo}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                        <div style="background-image: url({{imageThreeOffer}}) ;background-size: cover; width:100%; aspect-ratio: 2"></div>
                    <div Style='text-align:center; padding-bottom:30px'>
                            {# Speak to pain text 1#}
                            <br>{{offerThree}}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>   
        </div>

        <div class='campaign-justification skeleton block-full '>
            {# Justify consensus in the market for buying #}
            <div class='small-spacer mobile-spacer-med section-title-centered' style='padding-inline: 5%;' >
                {{justificationHeader}}
                </div>
            <div class='flex-columns flex-reverse-mobile large-spacer mobile-spacer-small' style='padding-left: 10%; padding-right:10%; padding-bottom:80px'>
                <div class='mobile-spacer-small' style='width:100%'>
                    {{justificationBody|safe}}
                </div>
                    <div class="mobile-spacer-small" style="background-image: url({{jusitificationImage}});background-size: cover; width:80%; aspect-ratio: 1.2"></div>
            </div>
            
        </div>

<div class='landing-justification skeleton block-full'>
            {# Justification why other people think we're great #}
            <!--Testimonials-->
            <div class="testimony-container">
                <!-- First Testimony -->
                <div class="flex-item-testimony">
                    <div class="testimony-speaker">
                    <div class="testimonial-head">
                        <img src="/images/testimonials/James-M.jpg">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="testimonial-name">James McCarthy</span><br>
                        <span class="testimonial-company"><b>Guardian Childcare</b></span>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-marks">
                    <span class="quote-marks">&ldquo;</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimony-text">
                    <p>Our business challenge was about how to connect with our families in a more proactive way.
                        We had no CRM, we had no formal database, we were using spreadsheets.
                        We weren't ready to invest in an off-the-shelf SAP or large-scale enterprise system.
                    <br><br>If your business is going through a period of change and you're uncertain about what
                        infrastructure to take on board&mdash;particularly from a technology point of view&mdash;<b>I can't recommend Rapid enough</b>.</p>  
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Second Testimony -->
                <div class="flex-item-testimony">
                    <div class="testimony-speaker">
                    <div class="testimonial-head">
                        <img src="/images/testimonials/Darryl-H.png">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="testimonial-name">Darryl Hopkins</span><br>
                        <span class="testimonial-company"><b>Torsion Homes</b></span>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-marks">
                    <span class="quote-marks">&ldquo;</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimony-text">
                    <p>Before Rapid we were using detailed Excel spreadsheets&mdash;I think a lot of people's file systems were probably their inbox.
                    Now it's compiled, it's easy to access, we can run reports on all of that data.
                    <br><br><b>It's a whole different world for us now.</b>
                    </p>
                    </div>
                </div>     
            </div>
        </div>


        {% include '../components/cta/knowmore.njk' %}
        
        </div> {# End of Wrap div #}
        {% include '../components/footer.njk' %}
    </body>
</html>
